7 qualify for the exemption provided for by this paragraph, the cost
8 of the items purchased by the qualified aircraft maintenance or
9 manufacturing facility shall equal or exceed the sum of Two Million
10 Dollars ($2,000,000.00);
11 17. Sales of tangible personal property consumed or
12 incorporated in the construction or expansion of a qualified
13 aircraft maintenance or manufacturing facility as defined in
14 paragraph 16 of this section. For purposes of this paragraph, sales
15 made to a contractor or subcontractor that has previously entered
16 into a contractual relationship with a qualified aircraft
